The paper discusses the recent developments in communication-efficient techniques for training and inference tasks in edge AI systems. This involves the use of machine learning algorithms (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), image classification (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), and distributed computing (cs.DC). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
